data.description: Tranquil Luxury Living with Spectacular Views & Endless Space! Exceptional 5-bed, 3-bath haven, nestled on nearly 10 acres of pure serenity just 5 mins from Hwy 395, past Chewelah, WA. This property offers a quiet retreat with stunning mountaintop views. Revel in the ambiance of a crackling fire and the occasional distant train whistle. 3200 sq ft of living space, this home offering the comfort of hardwood floors, granite countertops, a kitchen island, and a massive pantry, making meal preparation a joy. Park with ease in the oversized, detached 3-car garage/shop and utilize it for hobbies or storage. This property is set up to be perfect for horse lovers, with ample space for grazing and a welcoming environment for your four-legged friends. Enjoy a garden area w/deer fencing, set up for your green thumb. Fruit trees dot the landscape, providing fresh produce at your fingertips. Marvel at breathtaking views from your own mountaintop, while the property borders thousands of acres of timberland and peace!
